These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: drama, romance, horror
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, car, boat
1. the person watching drama movies is the person driving the car##1
2. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the car##1
3. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person watching romance movies##3
4. the person driving the car is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | horror | romance    |
| Transport     | car    | boat       | bus |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  software-developer, designer, architect
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, skiing, climbing
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
2. the architect is on the left of the software-developer##1
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far left or far right##3
4. the designer is the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |     2     |     3      |
| Job     | architect | software-developer | designer  |
| Sport   | biathlon  | skiing  | climbing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-3::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  dancer, project-manager, coach
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: house, disco, pop
1. the fan of disco is on the far left or far right##3
2. the dancer is on the far right##1
3. the project-manager is the fan of pop##1
4. the fan of disco is on the right of the fan of pop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Job           | coach | project-manager | dancer |
| Music-Genre   | house        | pop    | disco        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-4::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: reading, sudoku, photography
3 different pets are kept: hamster, goat, ferret
1. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
3. the owner of the hamster is between the person who's hobby is photography and the owner of the ferret##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Hobby   | photography | sudoku | reading |
| Pet     | goat  | hamster    | ferret  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-5::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: martial-arts, animation, documentary
The people use 3 different means of transport: trike, quad-bike, van
1. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
3. the person driving the van is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is between the person watching animation movies and the person driving the van##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | martial-arts | documentary |
| Transport     | quad-bike   | trike   | van   |

