.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-6::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: fishing, writing, rock-climbing
The people have 3 different jobs:  security-guard, writer, dressmaker
1. the dressmaker is on the left of the security-guard##1
2. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is fishing##3
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the writer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |   2    |     3      |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | fishing | writing      |
| Job     | writer  | dressmaker | security-guard |

