.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-7::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: pop, metal, disco
There are 3 different nationalities: pakistani, indonesian, nigerian
1. the fan of disco is on the right of the indonesian##1
2. the nigerian is on the left of the fan of pop##1
3. the nigerian is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |     3      |
| Music-Genre   | metal  | disco    | pop       |
| Nationality   | indonesian | nigerian | pakistani |

