.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-8::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, tea, lemonade
There 3 different types of food: onion, corn, tomato
1. the person drinking water is the person eating onion##1
2. the person eating corn is in the middle##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
4. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person eating onion##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |   3    |
| Beverage   | lemonade        | tea  | water   |
| Food       | tomato | corn | onion |

