2. the dutch is the person drinking milk##1
3. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
4. the canadian is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3    |
| Beverage      | milk    | soy-milk    | lemonade  |
| Nationality   | dutch | canadian | italian |

