.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-13::.
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, pakistani, indian
3 different pets are kept: mouse, frog, fish
1. the owner of the mouse is on the far left or far right##3
2. the indian is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
3. the owner of the fish is between the owner of the frog and the owner of the mouse##2
4. the owner of the mouse is the pakistani##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| Nationality   | canadian | indian | pakistani |
| Pet           | frog    | fish    | mouse       |

