.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-16::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery, animation
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, disco, r&b
1. the fan of disco is in the middle##1
2. the person watching animation movies is between the fan of r&b and the fan of dubstep##2
3. the fan of disco is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
4. the fan of r&b is the person watching disaster movies##1
5. the fan of dubstep is on the left or right of the person watching animation movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |     3     |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | animation | disaster |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep     | disco  | r&b    |

