.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, fanta, cola
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, mystery, family
1. the person watching mystery movies is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
2. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
3. the person drinking water is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
4. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |      3      |
| Beverage      | cola    | fanta | water         |
| Movie-Genre   | family | mystery  | epic |

 